{
  "stem": "26142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by coincidence-- I-- I just looked that up not too long ago that the-- the expulsion of the Jews in 19-- in 1492 from Spain, the edict that Isabella ordered was given out in the month of March.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they g-- they got four months to either convert or get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The last Jews left on Tisha B'av, which was August the 7-- the 2, 194-- 1492.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Columbus sailed to the United States a day later on-- after Tisha B'av on-- on August the 3, 1492.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's just a coincidence that all of these tragedies coincided at-- at the same day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there during the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took a walk around-- around the perimeters of the huge lumber yard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I noticed that there were a few-- a few of the-- of the lumbers, you know, the fence that were loose.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And with a good push, you can probably push it out and get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I-- and I still remember talking to my brother Tsvi and saying, let's-- let's try to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And his-- his answer was the same.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We're not going to leave Moshe and the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- the fact is, where would we have gone?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We thought that in Khust, there are still some.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, we stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We made our beds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody slept.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a-- a-- a-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the sky-- the sky was clear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the-- the-- the stars were out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were out on that field that night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were so many babies, children, how the parents tried to make comfortable for these children.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
